    <figure><img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/574cf4768a65e20cc7563c02/1548977489607-I58WGLKH16RGJ6Q1R92H/heuristics5.png" alt="Heuristics review — screen 5" loading="lazy" /></figure>
